KeyPad 7 = Decreases health by 100.
KeyPad 8 = Increases health by 100.
KeyPad 9 = Decreases maximum health by 100.
KeyPad + = Increases maximum health by 100.

KeyPad 4 = Decreases energy by 100.
KeyPad 5 = Increases energy by 100.
KeyPad 6 = Decreases maximum energy by 100.
KeyPad . = Increases maximum energy by 100.

KeyPad / = Set energy name to "blaze".
KeyPad * = Set energy name to "avenger".
KeyPad - = Set energy name to "monarch".

KeyPad 0 = Toggle God Mode.
KeyPad , = Suicide.
